 MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">2008] UKHL 27</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn63"></a><a href="#_ftnref63">[63]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">R (</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Feakins</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">) v Secretary of State for the Environment, Food and Rural Affairs </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">[2003] EWCA </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">Ci</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">v</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> 1546 [2004] 1 WLR 1761 at [23].</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn64"></a><a href="#_ftnref64">[64]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">S</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">ee, e.g. </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">R v Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, ex parte World Development Movement Ltd </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">[1995] 1 WLR 386.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn65"></a><a href="#_ftnref65">[65]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">See To Assist the Court: Third Party interventions in the UK, </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">Justice, October 2009.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn66"></a><a href="#_ftnref66">[66]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; fon