/contents"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#0000ff; font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline">Vol. 35 No. 17 · 12 September 2013</span></a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal"> </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">pp. 13-16 </span><a href="http://www.lrb.co.uk/v35/n17/stephen-sedley/beware-kite-flyers"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline">www.lrb.co.uk/v35/n17/stephen-sedley/beware-kite-flyers</span></a></h1><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn96"></a><a href="#_ftnref96">[96]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> Consultation paragraph 126.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn97"></a><a href="#_ftnref97">[97]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> Consultation paper paragraph 147.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn98"></a><a href="#_ftnref98">[98]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Morgan v Hinton Organics</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> [2009] EWCA </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">Civ</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> 107.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn99"></a><a href="#_ftnref99">[99]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> Civil Procedure R</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">ules Rule 45.43. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn100"></a><a href="#_ftnref100">[100]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Ibid</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn101"></a><a href="#_ftnref101">[101]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> See e.g.  </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Lassal</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> C-162/09.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn102"></a><a href="#_ftnref102">[102]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> See e.g. Rules of the Supreme Court, rule 35.1. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn103"></a><a href="#_ftnref103">[103]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">See </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Hamilton v Al Fayed</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> (No. 2) [2003]QB 1175.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn104"></a><a href="#_ftnref104">[104]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> See e.g. Rules of the Supreme Court, rule 46.3.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn105"></a><a href="#_ftnref105">[105]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">See </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Maaouia</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic"> v France </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">(2001) EHRR 42.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn106"></a><a href="#_ftnref106">[106]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Ibid.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn107"></a><a href="#_ftnref107">[107]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> See also </span><span style="f